Title: Schedule Week
Scope: KitchenAid
Level: User goal
Trigger: User wants to schedule their week's meals
Success guarantee: Week's Meals are planned.
Minimal guarantee: Fully input meals will be saved.
Main Success Scenario:
1. User _logs in_
2. User chooses day
3. User _adds meal_
4. User repeats steps 2-3 for each meal they want to plan

Extensions:
0a. Power loss
  0a1. System saves at each meal input or deletion.
1a. Unsuccessful login
  1a1. User _creates account_
  1a2. User _resets password/username_
3a. Meal already planned
  3a1. User edits planned meal
  3a2. User adds new meal
